arStrings.szText: Access the Season Journey through the {c_highlight}"SEASON" tab{/c} in the main menu.
The Season Journey will guide you through the {c_highlight}Seasonal experience{/c}. Complete objectives to earn {c_highlight}powerful rewards{/c}.
Complete the specified number of objectives in a Chapter to {c_highlight}unlock the Chapter rewards{/c} and progress to the next Chapter.
Make sure you {c_highlight}claim your Chapter rewards{/c} before the end of the season!
